Is it not possible to use inherited values in group defaults or do I have the code wrong? I can add inherited values with the following "inherited_value" code just fine in the exact field but when I try to set it in a group default I get an "invalid default value" error.

```"border_color": {
  "inherited_value": {
    "property_value_paths": {
      "color": "brand_settings.colors[1]"
    }
  }
}```
